00:32:28,480 --> 00:32:31,480
 and like everyone mentioned this thing.

507
00:32:31,480 --> 00:32:33,480
 They tried this with electricity

508
00:32:33,480 --> 00:32:38,480
 and that was kind of the incident for our industry

