00:32:38,480 --> 00:32:40,480
 where we got scared of this.

510
00:32:40,480 --> 00:32:45,480
 But then you can ask,

511
00:32:45,480 --> 00:32:50,480
 "Okay, but can we maybe use mostly electricity and some gas?"

